name: Alexander_Mid-Century_Living_Room_Collection_with_Tufted_Design
description:
This elegant Mid-Centuryl living room collection features a solid wood construction for stability and longevity, and a sinuous spring base for comfort and durability, oversized reversible down blend foam cushion seating upholstered in a fine oatmeal-beige linen blend fabric with deep tufting all around arms and back for an elegant transitional look. Legs are finished in a dark espresso color. Combine sofa, loveseat, and chair to complete the collection. Accent pillows included with Sofa and Love Seat only.
